  "Description": {
    "English": "Secure antimatter containment device, required before <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Antimatter</span> can be safely secured as <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Warp Cells</span>.<br><br>Rebound <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Oxygen</span> forms a protective gas pocket, preventing the antimatter from reacting with the surrounding casing.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "安全的反物质抑制设备，将<span class=\"name name-fuel\">反物质</span>安全作为<span class=\"name name-fuel\">曲速电池</span>的必须设备。<br><br>反弹的<span class=\"name name-fuel\">氧</span>形成保护性气囊，阻止反物质与周围套管产生反应。",
    "TencentChinese": "安全的反物质抑制设备，将<span class=\"name name-fuel\">反物质</span>安全作为<span class=\"name name-fuel\">曲速电池</span>的必须设备。<br><br>反弹的<span class=\"name name-fuel\">氧</span>形成保护性气囊，阻止反物质与周围套管产生反应。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "安全的反物質包覆裝置，得靠它才能將<span class=\"name name-fuel\">反物質</span>安全穩定為<span class=\"name name-fuel\">空間跳躍能量包</span>。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">氧氣</span>反彈形成防護氣罩，防止反物質與包覆頭罩發生作用。"
  },
